  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Hero’s Story Begins</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/9ebf915f6ed13ea3d1f2897ef74c5731.poster.avif?t=1742610523\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/9ebf915f6ed13ea3d1f2897ef74c5731.webm?t=1742610523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/9ebf915f6ed13ea3d1f2897ef74c5731.mp4?t=1742610523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Roxas Flare starts his day like any other but what danger lies inside this reality that he calls <strong>home</strong>.<br><br>Starting with headaches and a voice inside his head, Roxas must journey with close battlemates and newly acquired allies to save the land of Serith. For not all seems right in this noble land, for <strong>what is and what isn't</strong>, IS the real question.<br><br>Just another day to wake up to, another day of fighting to protect, another day for new attachments. Another day of  finding the <strong>truth</strong>.<br><br>Uncovering the mysteries is the ultimate adventure and the journey has only just begun!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/e44f5185fd8ec63cde376c7bd01c2e6f.poster.avif?t=1742610523\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/e44f5185fd8ec63cde376c7bd01c2e6f.webm?t=1742610523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/e44f5185fd8ec63cde376c7bd01c2e6f.mp4?t=1742610523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/ec6b7cae7c75630154d21e6b32890f30.poster.avif?t=1742610523\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/ec6b7cae7c75630154d21e6b32890f30.webm?t=1742610523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/ec6b7cae7c75630154d21e6b32890f30.mp4?t=1742610523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Embark on a thrilling adventure of over 10 hours of gameplay!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fully voiced from the main cast, to the NPCs. Even the cat has a voice</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gain new party members to complete your quest</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Learn new abilities that will help you on your mission</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Battle and destroy many different foes</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/0f4b55b7cd1c93f0f12b79aa4ae31c0b.poster.avif?t=1742610523\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/0f4b55b7cd1c93f0f12b79aa4ae31c0b.webm?t=1742610523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/0f4b55b7cd1c93f0f12b79aa4ae31c0b.mp4?t=1742610523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Old-school style RPG to enjoy a nostalgic tale</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Turn-based battles with side view characters</li></ul><br>Enjoy the First 2 Arcs Of the story<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/1c41690d0b2efb8703b339577b594755.poster.avif?t=1742610523\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/1c41690d0b2efb8703b339577b594755.webm?t=1742610523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/1c41690d0b2efb8703b339577b594755.mp4?t=1742610523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/560af5326b61da1eb742b409f5605fd0.poster.avif?t=1742610523\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/560af5326b61da1eb742b409f5605fd0.webm?t=1742610523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/560af5326b61da1eb742b409f5605fd0.mp4?t=1742610523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Characters</h2><br><u>Roxas</u>- Knight of Serith <strong>/</strong>   <u>Aiki</u>- The Neko Knight<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/43ebaade29a37707f47c9ba85e17b973.avif?t=1742610523\" width=154 height=172 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906920/extras/8adc4b4740ca785cd5356a1853d73872.avif?t=1742610523\" width=154 height=172 /></span>",
